name: Behind Blue Eyes
wikiSummary: "Behind Blue Eyes" is covered by Limp Bizkit on their album Results May Vary, released in 2003. The song was released for the film Gothika starring Halle Berry. The song is originally written by Pete Townshend of The Who.
